    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Very good work, lots of small and big chores here!\n\nI think the right tag would be refactor since we are using a new token, style being only \"Changes that do not affect the meaning of the code (white-space, formatting, missing semi-colons, etc)\" (https://github.com/angular/angular.js/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#commit)\n\nBut: no big deal having 3 commits etc.. WFM\n",
